nd_of_Sealskin_Point\" title=\"House Farwynd of Sealskin Point\">Farwynd of Sealskin Point</a><sup>GW</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\">Goodbrother of Hammerhorn</a><sup>GW</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother_of_Shatterstone\" title=\"House Goodbrother of Shatterstone\">Goodbrother of Shatterstone</a><sup>OW</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw\" title=\"House Harlaw\">Harlaw of Harlaw</a><sup>H</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Kenning_of_Harlaw\" title=\"House Kenning of Harlaw\">Kenning of Harlaw</a><sup>H</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Merlyn\" title=\"House Merlyn\">Merlyn</a><sup>GW</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Myre\" title=\"House Myre\">Myre</a><sup>H</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Orkwood\" title=\"House Orkwood\">Orkwood</a><sup>O</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Saltcliffe\" title=\"House Saltcliffe\">Saltcliffe</a><sup>S</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Sparr\" title=\"House Sparr\">Sparr</a><sup>GW</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stonehouse\" title=\"House Stonehouse\">Stonehouse</a><sup>OW</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stonetree\" title=\"House Stonetree\">Stonetree</a><sup>H</sup></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sunderly</a><sup>S</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tawney\" title=\"House Tawney\">Tawney</a><sup>O</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Volmark\" title=\"House Volmark\">Volmark</a><sup>H</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wynch\" title=\"House Wynch\">Wynch</a><sup>P</sup></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Masterly/<br />Knightly Houses</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Har